Summary: Sathee, which means Companion in Hindi, is a friendly AI-powered chatbot developed for the elderly. A study found that more than 40% of seniors experience the feeling of loneliness. Sathee can detect a user's mood or emotion through text, and then provides relevant recommendations and responses to improve their mood. name: AI Club
Summary: Data Science and Artificial Intelligence are the two important technologies in the world today.Data science is an inter-disciplinary field that uses scientific methods, processes, algorithms, and systems to extract knowledge and insights from many structural and unstructured data. Data science is related to data mining, machine learning and big data.Artificial intelligence (AI) is intelligence demonstrated by machines, unlike the natural intelligence displayed by humans and animals, which involves consciousness and emotionality. This session is organized by SLASSCOM TechKids program to introduce Data Science and Artificial intelligence to school students. All the registered kids will receive the opportunity to discuss with the trainers and ask questions about data science and artificial intelligence during the session. We hope to do an interesting exercise during the session to build an Artificial Intelligence to detect your mood!Please fill the registration form given in this URL (http://bit.ly/Intaifeb) before 5th March. You will receive the zoom link for the session in an email.Date: 7th March 2021Time: 7.30pm to 8.30pmMode: 100% online (via Zoom)
